div.font-family: Linux Libertine, Hoefler Text, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif

input.transition: background 0.1s ease, border-color 0.1s ease, box-shadow 0.1s ease

circle.transition: stroke-dashoffset 750ms cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.6, 0.32, 1.6), stroke-dasharray 750ms cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.6, 0.32, 1.6), transform 375ms cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.6, 0.32, 1.6)
